WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.439
You're actually a witch.

2
00:00:02.439 --> 00:00:04.040
I'm a witch.

3
00:00:04.040 --> 00:00:04.879
Yes.

4
00:00:04.879 --> 00:00:09.640
Your power to turn wishes into reality is unmatched.

5
00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:12.160
Perhaps the greatest of your generation,

6
00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:14.759
but you must be careful.

7
00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:16.480
Careful of what?

8
00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:18.559
Never underestimate human greed

9
00:00:18.559 --> 00:00:20.559
and their loss for blood.

10
00:00:20.559 --> 00:00:21.719
I have to protect you.

11
00:00:23.739 --> 00:00:29.280
So my dreams have something to do with me being a witch.

12
00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:32.859
Those dreams are your fate.

13
00:00:32.859 --> 00:00:37.500
I could only conceal them from you until you have a 30th birthday.

14
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:45.460
Heh, the body.

15
00:00:45.460 --> 00:00:50.000
Vigorous male, there seems to be a pentagram drawn underneath him.

16
00:00:50.000 --> 00:00:54.619
Like performing a ritual?

17
00:00:54.619 --> 00:00:58.340
I would something like this happen, today of all days.

18
00:00:58.340 --> 00:01:01.060
So many people watching, we need to cover this up.

19
00:01:01.060 --> 00:01:02.299
Don't interfere.

20
00:01:02.299 --> 00:01:04.260
This has nothing to do with us.

21
00:01:04.260 --> 00:01:08.299
Corpse at a wedding is sure to catch the police's attention.

22
00:01:08.299 --> 00:01:11.700
That detective Hank, handle it.

23
00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:12.980
Are you sure?

24
00:01:12.980 --> 00:01:14.859
If the police discover I received it.

25
00:01:18.299 --> 00:01:21.540
Tonight's feast was meant to be that brazen bride of yours,

26
00:01:21.540 --> 00:01:40.379
it seems we'll have to delay the hunt and sacrifice.

27
00:01:40.379 --> 00:01:46.129
Dealing with humans makes magic seem easy.

28
00:01:46.129 --> 00:01:56.500
Don't worry, I'll take care of you.

29
00:01:56.500 --> 00:01:59.439
She doesn't know what I do, she truly is.

30
00:01:59.439 --> 00:02:01.439
You're the danger she's in.

